data.description: Beautiful home that just needs your finishing touch! Just over 2,000 square feet and no city taxes!  This 4 bedroom 2 bath home offers plenty of space to kick back and relax in the cozy living room or in the huge bonus room with a bar! Don't miss this opportunity to have a home in an established neighborhood with modern updates!Sellelr will pay for flooring in living room, foyer, hall, and kitchen to be repaired and installed by a licensed GC with an accepted offer.
